{"tid":1036761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩《Pokémon Go》走甩精靈 男子怒打警察被捕","createTime":"2019-02-25T12:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T12:28:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c8340a54a51b8c62fa5a799476bfe722778e1f","tid":1036761,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190224/photo/bkn-20190224150223094-0224_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190224152524\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190224150223094-0224_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190224152524&h=f6aac8e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本仍有不少《Pok&eacute;mon Go》支持者，在街上到處捉精靈。（互聯網）<br />\n日本愛嬡縣上周六（23日）有一名男子，因現手機遊戲捉精靈失敗，怒打一名被指騷擾他的男警，結果被押返警署，控以妨礙公務罪名。惟該男子一直否認打人，事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，涉事男子40歲，事發時正在玩《Pok&eacute;mon Go》。據悉，東松山市警署下午3時許接到千舟町一間酒店報案，指酒店外有50多人聚集游蕩，阻礙出入。2名警員到場了解，得悉是一批來捉罕有精靈的「訓練員」，於是勸眾人離開。當男警員接觸涉事男子時，後者突然大叫「你累我隻精靈走甩咗！」並向警員揮拳攻擊，結果當場被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190224/bkn-20190224150223094-0224_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190224%2Fbkn-20190224150223094-0224_00912_001.html&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8Q2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=f5ccc6b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190224/bkn-20190224150223094-0224_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c1159fd227a9d0f7a60e9de6f2933c5c0aabd275","tid":1036761,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:28:34.000Z","msg":"日本人"}]}